      • setEllipsoid

        public void setEllipsoid(Target.TARGET target)
        Sets the current ellipsoid to that of an non-Earth body. This method can only be called using the CUSTOM ellipsoid, otherwise it will have no effect.
        Parameters:
        target - The target.
